modules.description: This module manages communication with HID devices through operations like `enumerate`, `open_id`, and `open_path` to discover and open devices, and `read` and `write` to transfer data. It works with device identifiers, paths, and raw data buffers, supporting both blocking and nonblocking modes. Concrete use cases include interacting with game controllers, USB sensors, and custom HID hardware by sending and receiving HID reports.
